Description: Utility programs for the libbzdev-java package
 This package contains the programs lsnof and scrunner,
 and man pages for both. These programs use a configuration
 file scrunner.conf, typically located in /etc/bzdev. lsnof
 generates documentation for instances of the class
 org.bzdev.obnaming.NamedObjectFactory, and scrunner allows
